---
import Container from "./Container.astro";

---

<div id="solution">
    <Container>
      <div class="space-y-6 justify-between text-gray-600 md:flex flex-row-reverse md:gap-6 md:space-y-0 lg:gap-12 lg:items-center">
        <div class="md:5/12 lg:w-1/2">
          <img
            src="./images/pie.png"
            alt="image"
            loading="lazy"
            width=""
            height=""
            class="w-full"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="md:7/12 lg:w-1/2">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 md:text-4xl dark:text-white">
            Unleashing the Power of Fast, Secure, and Stunning Ecommerce
          </h2>
          <p class="my-8 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            In developing the Parcomtel eCommerce website, we focused on creating a front-end with a visually appealing and unique user interface (UI) to provide an exceptional user experience. The front-end, also known as the client-side, encompasses everything that users directly interact with.<br/>
            we implemented fast and secure technologies to ensure seamless functionality and data management, to facilitate smooth communication between various system components.<br/>
            By integrating these technologies, we have strived to create a cohesive and high-performing eCommerce platform that not only meets but exceeds user expectations, providing a secure, efficient, and visually engaging online shopping experience.
          </p>
          <div class="divide-y space-y-4 divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-800">
            <div class="mt-8 flex gap-4 md:items-center">
              <div class="w-14 h-14 flex gap-4 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900/20">
